title: Let Go of the Pain
itunes:title: Let Go of the Pain
description:
Episode 413 -  We humans, for some reason, love to hold on to what holds us back. We love to hold on to the misery that should stay in the past. In this episode, I teach how to overcome the pain of what has happened in the past.
